sequenceDiagram
  participant H as Harness (Codex/Claude/Cowork)
  participant M as agentsuite-mcp
  participant A as FounderAgent
  participant D as Disk (.agentsuite/)
  participant L as LLM Provider

  H->>M: founder_run(business_goal, inputs_dir)
  M->>A: agent.run(request, run_id)
  A->>D: write inputs_manifest.json
  A->>L: extract prompt
  L-->>A: JSON context
  A->>D: write extracted_context.json
  loop for each of 9 spec artifacts
    A->>L: spec prompt
    L-->>A: markdown
    A->>D: write <artifact>.md
  end
  A->>L: consistency_check prompt
  L-->>A: mismatches JSON
  A->>D: write consistency_report.json
  A->>D: render 11 brief templates
  A->>L: qa_score prompt
  L-->>A: scores JSON
  A->>D: write qa_report.md
  A-->>M: state(stage="approval")
  M-->>H: RunResult(status="awaiting_approval", primary_path)

  Note over H: human reviews brand-system.md
  H->>M: founder_approve(run_id, approver, project_slug)
  M->>A: agent.approve(...)
  A->>D: copy artifacts to _kernel/<slug>/
  A-->>M: state(stage="done")
  M-->>H: ApprovalResult(promoted_paths)
